refinedPrompt: Create a responsive webpage that displays a list of vegetables and fruits with their respective prices. Each item should have an "Add to Cart" button. The webpage should have a clean and appealing design, with a header containing the website name and a navigation menu. Implement a shopping cart functionality that allows users to add items to their cart, view the cart contents, and proceed to checkout. Ensure the website is mobile-friendly and follows web accessibility guidelines.
